~FT--==--==--==->-==--==--==-<-==--==--==--==--==--==-<-==--==--==->-==--==--==--
~FYCommand Name~CB:~RS record
~FT--==--==--==->-==--==--==-<-==--==--==--==--==--==-<-==--==--==->-==--==--==--
Command Usage: .record [user]
  
Synopsis:
  Displays the arrest record of a user. Any time they have had a staff
  command used against them, it gets recorded in this log, which makes
  it helpful in finding the user's who like nothing more than to get
  into trouble. You can also view comments that have been added by
  other staff members via the '.addhist' command, in regarding to the
  specified user.
~FT--==--==--==->-==--==--==-<-==--==--==--==--==--==-<-==--==--==->-==--==--==--

